       _v_._r_e_c_l_a_s_s allows a user to create a new vector map based on the reclas-
       sification  of  an  existing vector map.  The user provides the program
       with a category conversion file, input vector map name, an output  vec-
       tor  map  name,  and  the type of input map.  There is an option (d) to
       dissolve common boundaries between adjoining map areas of the same  re-
       classed category value.


       NNoottee::  The  dissolve  option will work on only those areas which are of
       the same conversion category value.  If a map area is inside (island) a
       converted  area  and is NOT converted to the same value, its boundaries
       are output to the resultant map.

